     C                   MOVEL     'SDSECDKDSP'  DBPGM
     C                   MOVE      '1'           *INU7
     C                   MOVE      '1'           *INU8
     C                   MOVE      '1'           *INLR
     C                   DUMP
      *
      **  Terminate the program
      *
     C                   RETURN
      *
     C                   ENDSR
